http://id.loc.gov/ontologies/bflc/aap.@value: Maas, Sarah J. The world of Throne of glass

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: "Everyone knows the story of the assassin queen. But now, fans of the Throne of Glass series will be immersed in Aelin's journey like never before. From Adarlan's dark past to Terrasen's bright future, this comprehensive illustrated guide will bring the people, creatures, settings, magic, gods, and world of Aelin's epic story to life with eight pages of stunning full-color illustrations and descriptive portrayals. Complete with an expansive vocabulary and timeline of events, this is the must-have official companion to the Throne of Glass series"-- Provided by publisher.
